<HEADLINE>
<P>
REASONS FOR S&amp;L CRISIS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
To quote from The Times: "The S&amp;L calamity will cost the average American 
family more than $20 a month for the next 30 years," and, "Vice President 
George Bush headed a task force on 'regulation of financial services' that 
could have plugged the hole as early as 1983." 
</P>
<P>
Read my lips, indeed! 
</P>
<P>
PETER M. WILLIAMS 
</P>
<P>
Del Mar 
</P>
