DEPARTMENT; LYNWOOD (CA); POLICE BRUTALITY; POLICE MISCONDUCT; POLICE COMMUNITY 
RELATIONS; LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS; POLICE SHOOTINGS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; 
