<P>
MCGRUFF TO APPEAR AT PLAZA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
McGruff, the Crime Prevention Dog, will make his annual appearance at the Plaza 
Pasadena on Friday, Saturday and Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
Throughout each day, he will sing songs, hand out coloring books and give 
safety advice to children. 
</P>
<P>
The Pasadena Police Department will show off a helicopter, patrol car and 
motorcycle. The Fire Department will have a truck on hand. And youngsters older 
than 3 will be fingerprinted for free. 
