<P>
MURDERS -- ORANGE COUNTY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA092790-0200 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 284113 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 27, 1990, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
