Hills Finds Airbus Loan 'Disturbing': U.S. Trade Representative Carla Anderson 
Hills, who is complaining about European subsidies to Airbus Industrie, finds a 
loan that the jet maker made to Northwest Airlines "particularly disturbing," a 
spokeswoman said. 
</P>
