Northwest to buy 75 jets built by Airbus, a four-nation European consortium. In 
a Sept. 14 letter to the European Community, Hills said she wants 
"clarification and information" about the loan as soon as possible, said 
spokeswoman Torie Clarke. Representatives of Airbus and the European Community 
deny that the loan was unfair. 
